These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, july, january, november
1. the person who's birthday is in july is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in november is between the person who's birthday is in march and the person who's birthday is in july##2
3. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Birthday   | march | november | july | january |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, drama, epic, adventure
1. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
2. the person watching drama movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the person watching superhero movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | superhero | adventure | epic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, bluemaster, oliveros, vegafina
1. the vegafina-smoker is on the left or right of the baccarat-smoker##3
2. the baccarat-smoker is in an odd position##4
3. the oliveros-smoker is between the vegafina-smoker and the bluemaster-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Cigar   | baccarat | vegafina | oliveros | bluemaster |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-4::.
City: venice, berlin, liverpool, miami
1. the person traveling to berlin is on the left or right of the person traveling to venice##3
2. the person traveling to liverpool is in an even position##4
3. the person traveling to miami is between the person traveling to venice and the person traveling to liverpool##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |       3       |   4    |
| City   | berlin | venice | miami | liverpool |

