.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, d&b, punk, techno
1. the fan of salsa is in an even position##4
2. the fan of punk is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
3. the fan of d&b is on the left or right of the fan of punk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | techno | salsa | punk | d&b |

