.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-14::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, september, june, october
1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3
3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
4. the person who's birthday is in october is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Birthday   | june | october | july | september |

