1. the dutch is on the right of the japanese##1
2. the indian is in an even position##4
3. the japanese is on the right of the pakistani##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1      |   2    |    3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | pakistani | japanese | dutch | indian |

