.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, salsa, punk, dubstep
1. the fan of punk is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the fan of punk##1
3. the fan of punk is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |         2          |    3    |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | pop | dubstep | punk | salsa |

 